### Generate TTS - Normal Request
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/tts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "مرحباً بك في عالم البرمجة المتقدمة.",
  "voice": "ar-SA-HamedNeural",
  "rate": "+0%"
}

### Generate TTS - Empty Text
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/tts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "   \n  ",
  "voice": "ar-SA-HamedNeural",
  "rate": "+0%"
}

### Generate TTS - Invalid Voice
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/tts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "تجربة",
  "voice": "invalid-voice-name",
  "rate": "+0%"
}